name: Mighty Jabba
Lore: 'Hutt leader of notorious criminal organization. Gangster of the vilest ilk. Would rather forfeit a fortune in cash than risk one whisper attesting to his mercy.',
Text: 'Deploys -2 to a Jabba''s Palace site. When with your alien leader, adds one battle destiny. May escort a captive. To use his landspeed requires +1 Force. May not be targeted by weapons unless your other aliens present are each ''hit''. Immune to attrition < 4.',
